    <svcsubproc>
        <title>Mud Guards</title>
        <para>The mud guards at the rear of the bus body are an available option. The optional mud guards located at the
            front wheel fender extension (
            <hotlnk document="s47006_6.xml" xrefid="f4700617">Figure 17, Item 1</hotlnk>).
        </para>
        <para>To remove the rear mud guards:</para>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Locate the mounting bolts and reinforcing bar at the rear wheel well.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Loosen and remove the mounting nuts and bolts.</para>
        </step1>
        <step1>
            <para count="1">Remove the reinforcing bar.</para>
        </step1>
    </svcsubproc>
